document_data.History:
Some scholars suspected that tweens were once members of a race that inhabited the [[Outlands]] known as the [[kyleen]], who had fled to the ethereal plane after a strange chaos plague transformed them.

In the {{YearlinkName|1357}}, tweens were known to be lurking around the [[Shadowdale]] region.

In the {{YearlinkName|1368}}, a group of [[Beshaban]]s operating a shrine in the [[sewers of Ravens Bluff]], that included [[Cleo of Bad Luck]] and [[Tinsel Reltether]], were all hosts to tweens.<ref>{{Cite organized play/LC/Luck Takes a Vacation|10-12}}
